# read N
N = int(input())
# read list
L = list(map(int, input().split()))

# create dictionary for numbers
D = {}
for i in L:
    D[i] = D.get(i, 0) + 1

# create list of numbers
X = []
for i in D:
    if D[i] % 2 == 1:
        X.append(i)

# print numbers
print(X[0], X[1])

N = int(input())
divisors = list(map(int, input().split()))
x = 1
y = 1
for i in range(N):
    if divisors[i] == 1:
        continue
    if divisors[i] == divisors[i + 1]:
        x *= divisors[i]
        i += 1
    else:
        y *= divisors[i]
print(x, y)
print(x, y)
